{"tid":1503762,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰略］對於日後（勇）遊戲的小小攻略","createTime":"2019-08-25T05:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T05:45:47.000Z","uid":143642,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"23184e898cd1c95bd8b64a495ff2bc19f41407b8","tid":1503762,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"以下遊戲內容 如有雷同 實屬巧合<br />\n<br />\n<strong>攻略目的：討論及改善玩法</strong><br />\n利申：前中後均有嘗試 非冷氣軍師<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">個人認為現時玩法缺點：</span><br />\n1. 防線太脆弱<br />\n2. 浪費制高點<br />\n3. 前排撤退艱難<br />\n<br />\n以下簡單講下我建議<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">防線</span><br />\n個人覺得防線用作拖延時間 防守為主 <br />\n頭一排水馬/類似物件 企高 等玩家利用黎擋子彈<br />\n不遮擋視線<br />\n第二排陷阱 唔要3角鐵馬 要訓低鐵馬 鐵馬之間索帶<br />\n利用鐵馬罅隙/放置物件等能令敵人行動受阻 （hit!)<br />\n及後自由發揮（波子/油/繩索等等）<br />\n留單一較窄位置比真勇玩家守（睇情況）<br />\n<br />\n第二條防線？係咪多左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係第一條防線設置到9成 睇場地 附近物資 加大家意見 係第一防線較近地方設置 線與線中間放物件（自由發揮）全體二線後hit and run 再攞多啲時間撤退<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">制高點</span><br />\n一定要利用 唔好再食花生<br />\n大聲公哨兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已有<br />\n遠攻 中後排玩家派發作遠攻物品（水彈/雞蛋等等不要硬物 怕tk）<br />\n<br />\n一旦敵人舉槍 投擲向舉槍敵人（小心玩家及報導員）遮擋視線/令槍支失效更好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前線撤退</span><br />\n敵人突如其來進攻 前線先走 再到中排 後到後排 <br />\n即使留有位置亦會積聚 前線都不可能用最快速度逃跑 <br />\n建議中排留出更大空間  滅火隊唔好用水 作用不大 <br />\n成支都未必熄一個 加上要冒著煙淋熄 用鐵蓋/鐵碟/掟向冇人地方更好 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>其實防線拖延到更多時間即可解決</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">遊戲最重要係咩？當然係玩家啦</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打狗！救人！</span><br />\n冇得驚啦 唔好再怕 唔要再驚恐式逃跑！"},{"pid":"436628e9704ef81c6cab0ea6020d54f8ea631583","tid":1503762,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"a3c90957fd650f9dc0bb1b0abb4be36f00ba1f93","tid":1503762,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:34:27.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"6af3f0f9c9315c4758a5b77ab0919a6da418af83","tid":1503762,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:34:37.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"ec085a3a54a83244262650d4c89c6124f5a9ab7d","tid":1503762,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:34:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,未必CALL 到人, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全部1點，唯一底線，唔衝禁區(會變恐襲)</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚都要讓路!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日826 仲有國泰城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bdbee85f02e4c37ee5543a7aa98d1ffab5e774","tid":1503762,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:34:47.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"716b83c7b060769ba47f0202f365e06a497dacea","tid":1503762,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"45752433b51e2ca0554135c1952003a7d1838990","tid":1503762,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:35:07.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"fa7492f4963842fab2f2ff95cb08498393406b09","tid":1503762,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:35:24.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"26318612b13204efae4168271ab6e71c7efdea5b","tid":1503762,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"a350917e00c884a7976ad1455361f04a9f694b61","tid":1503762,"uid":143642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:35:44.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pi